metadata.name: COLORFUL MELANIN
metadata.description:
It was given to us by the Most High. 
It all started with that gift that is inherited only from us; 
That we have given the world a bewitching and seductive formula.
From creamy vanilla to voluptuous ebony.
A rainbow of melanin. 
We are the light and the dark here on mother earth. We shine in the sun and we shine in the moonlight.
We are the rulers of the earth and the creators of life.
Thank goodness for shades of melanin.
